Description: Limestone ostracon: on recto and verso respectively six lines and one line of an administrative text containing a list of deliveries of vegetables by the chief of Medjai Mentuemheb.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: J. J. Černy and A.H. Gardiner, ‘Hieratic Ostraca’ (Oxford 1957), p. 16 and pl. LV, 3; K. Kitchen, 'Ramesside Inscriptions' I (Oxford 1975), 369; 'idem', 'Ramesside Inscriptions, Translated and Annotated: Translations' I (Oxford 1993), p. 305.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (136400) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/136400)
